snippet.title: Unworthy | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Get Unworthy on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/613190/Unworthy/

Robbed of life and unworthy of death, a nameless warrior wanders a ruined landscape in search of meaning...
Game launches to PC on May 29th, 2018 for $14.99 USD. News on console releases in the future.

Follow the game on our social media pages to get the latest news:
▶️Official Website: http://www.unworthygame.com/
▶️Unworthy's Facebook Page: https://www.facebook.com/UnworthyGame/
▶️Unworthy's Subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/UnworthyTheGame/
▶️Developer's Twitter: https://twitter.com/mramlice
▶️Discord: https://discord.gg/GBACwyQ
